James Lance https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Lance 0 James Frederick Grenville Lance (born 29 September 1974 in Southampton, Hampshire) is an English actor, best known for his appearances in a number of British comedy series. He also starred in the 2009 ITV drama Boy Meets Girl, alongside Martin Freeman.
